name: Unknown Soldier
description:
This photo was taken in Chatillon en Diois, a small French mountain village, in November 2021. It represents a death monument in honor of the men of the village who died during the first and second world wars.

This photo is a special edition made available for a limited period of time for the end of the year celebrations in 2021.

You can find all my photos at : https://samuelboivin.fr/

Samuel Boivin
